author: By Chris Greenwood for the Daily Mail, Zoie O'brien For Mailonline and Sebastian Murphy-bates For Mailonline
title: Singer, 22, has fallen to her death from luxury London apartment block
description: An aspiring singer has died after falling from the Heron building in London, sparking a police murder probe. Bethany-Maria Beales was described as a 'shining star' by her family.
